---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Vitaly Executive Chauffeur — how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
>
  <section class="pt-44 pb-32 px-6 lg:px-16">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <p class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.42em] uppercase text-stone-600 mb-8">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif font-light italic text-ivory-100 text-4xl mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-stone-700 mb-16">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-12 text-stone-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif font-light text-ivory-200 text-xl mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>We collect information you provide when making a booking or enquiry, including your name, email address, phone number, and travel details.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif font-light text-ivory-200 text-xl mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>Your information is used solely to arrange and manage your bookings, respond to enquiries, and improve our service. We do not sell or share your data with third parties.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif font-light text-ivory-200 text-xl mb-4">3. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>We retain your personal data only as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes outlined in this policy, or as required by law.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif font-light text-ivory-200 text-xl mb-4">4. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>Under GDPR, you have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@vitalychauffeur.com" class="text-brass-500 link-underline">info@vitalychauffeur.com</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif font-light text-ivory-200 text-xl mb-4">5. Contact</h2>
          <p>For any privacy-related queries, contact Vitaly Executive Chauffeur at <a href="mailto:info@vitalychauffeur.com" class="text-brass-500 link-underline">info@vitalychauffeur.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
